---
import FadeIn from "./FadeIn.astro";
---

<section class="bg-slate-50 py-20 px-6 font-manrope">
  <!-- Emotional Hook -->
  <FadeIn effect="fade" delay={0}>
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center mb-20">
      <h2
        class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-extrabold text-slate-900 leading-tight"
      >
        Tired of Confusing MRI Choices and Costs?
      </h2>

      <p class="text-lg sm:text-xl text-slate-600 mt-6">
        You’re told you need an MRI. But where do you go? What’s the real cost?
        Will the scan be good enough?
      </p>

      <ul
        class="mt-6 space-y-2 text-slate-600 text-md text-left sm:text-center sm:max-w-xl sm:mx-auto"
      >
        <li>
          • Searching online. Calling random centers. Hoping for the best.
        </li>
        <li>• Insurance games. Unknown prices. Delayed results.</li>
        <li>• It shouldn’t be this hard to get care.</li>
      </ul>

      <p class="text-lg sm:text-xl text-slate-700 font-medium mt-6">
        <strong>Clarity changes that.</strong> Our SmartMatch<sup>™</sup> system
        connects you with trusted imaging centers — matched to your diagnosis, location,
        and preferences.
      </p>
    </div>
  </FadeIn>

  <!-- How It Works -->
  <FadeIn effect="zoom" delay={200}>
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center mt-16 mb-20">
      <h3 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold text-blue-900 tracking-tight">
        How Clarity Works — Simple, Seamless, Smart
      </h3>
      <div class="mt-4 w-24 h-1 bg-yellow-400 mx-auto rounded-full"></div>
      <p class="text-lg sm:text-xl text-slate-600 mt-6 leading-relaxed">
        From the moment you're told you need an MRI, we handle the complexity.
        No more phone tag, insurance surprises, or guesswork. Just the right
        scan — at the right center — at the right price.
      </p>
    </div>
  </FadeIn>

  <!-- Step Cards -->
  <div
    class="grid gap-8 grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 px-4 sm:px-0"
  >
    <FadeIn effect="slide-up" delay={300}>
      <div
        class="flex flex-col justify-between h-full min-h-[320px] bg-white p-6 rounded-xl border-2 border-[#e6c378] shadow-md hover:shadow-lg transition-all text-left"
      >
        <div class="text-4xl mb-4">🩺</div>
        <h4 class="text-lg font-bold text-slate-800 mb-2">
          Tell Us What You Need
        </h4>
        <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
          Pick your scan — like a brain, knee, or spine MRI. No referral needed.
        </p>
      </div>
    </FadeIn>

    <FadeIn effect="slide-up" delay={400}>
      <div
        class="flex flex-col justify-between h-full min-h-[320px] bg-white p-6 rounded-xl border-2 border-[#e6c378] shadow-md hover:shadow-lg transition-all text-left"
      >
        <div class="text-4xl mb-4">📍</div>
        <h4 class="text-lg font-bold text-slate-800 mb-2">
          Get Matched Instantly
        </h4>
        <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
          Our SmartMatch™ engine pairs you with the best center based on your
          needs.
        </p>
      </div>
    </FadeIn>

    <FadeIn effect="slide-up" delay={500}>
      <div
        class="flex flex-col justify-between h-full min-h-[320px] bg-white p-6 rounded-xl border-2 border-[#e6c378] shadow-md hover:shadow-lg transition-all text-left"
      >
        <div class="text-4xl mb-4">💳</div>
        <h4 class="text-lg font-bold text-slate-800 mb-2">
          Know Your Price Upfront
        </h4>
        <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
          See transparent pricing. Pay online to reserve. No surprises, ever.
        </p>
      </div>
    </FadeIn>

    <FadeIn effect="slide-up" delay={600}>
      <div
        class="flex flex-col justify-between h-full min-h-[320px] bg-white p-6 rounded-xl border-2 border-[#e6c378] shadow-md hover:shadow-lg transition-all text-left"
      >
        <div class="text-4xl mb-4">📄</div>
        <h4 class="text-lg font-bold text-slate-800 mb-2">
          Receive Fast Results
        </h4>
        <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
          Board-certified radiologists read your scan. Results come securely,
          quickly.
        </p>
      </div>
    </FadeIn>
  </div>
</section>
